</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="5DCA0485FFC0FFBEB1AD557CFB16FC06" pageId="79" pageNumber="80" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="156F570EFFC0FFBEB1AD557CFA2BFC4E" blockId="79.[151,1437,151,969]" pageId="79" pageNumber="80">
<emphasis id="27A48B1CFFC0FFBEB1AD557CFEE4FCF7" bold="true" box="[199,328,798,824]" pageId="79" pageNumber="80">Comments</emphasis>
: The Iranian specimens of 
<taxonomicName id="D2D02C8DFFC0FFBEB31C557DFC8EFCF6" baseAuthorityName="Kiritshenko" baseAuthorityYear="1936" box="[630,802,799,825]" class="Insecta" family="Pseudococcidae" genus="Peliococcus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="79" pageNumber="80" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chersonensis">
<emphasis id="27A48B1CFFC0FFBEB31C557DFC8EFCF6" box="[630,802,799,825]" italics="true" pageId="79" pageNumber="80">P. chersonensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
differ from the descriptions by 
<bibRefCitation id="71412AFFFFC0FFBEB5E8557DFAC1FCF6" author="Ter-Grigorian, M. A." box="[1154,1389,799,825]" pageId="79" pageNumber="80" refId="ref97227" refString="Ter-Grigorian, M. A. (1973) Fauna of the Armenian SSR: Scale insects (Coccoidea, Pseudococcidae). Akademii Nauk Armiansky SSR, Erevan, 246 pp." type="book" year="1973">Ter-Grigorian (1973)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="71412AFFFFC0FFBEB1FD5521FE96FC92" author="Danzig, E. M." box="[151,314,835,861]" pageId="79" pageNumber="80" pagination="123 - 154" refId="ref87582" refString="Danzig, E. M. (2001) Mealybugs of the genera Peliococcus and Peliococcopsis from Russia and neighbouring countries (Homoptera: Coccinea: Pseudococcidae). Zoosystematica Rossica, 9 (1), 123 - 154." type="journal article" year="2001">Danzig (2001)</bibRefCitation>
in having dorsal clusters of multilocular pores present only on the abdominal segments; those in the descriptions by 
<bibRefCitation id="71412AFFFFC0FFBEB0225505FD98FC4E" author="Ter-Grigorian, M. A." box="[328,564,871,897]" pageId="79" pageNumber="80" refId="ref97227" refString="Ter-Grigorian, M. A. (1973) Fauna of the Armenian SSR: Scale insects (Coccoidea, Pseudococcidae). Akademii Nauk Armiansky SSR, Erevan, 246 pp." type="book" year="1973">Ter-Grigorian (1973)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="71412AFFFFC0FFBEB3015505FCA1FC4E" author="Danzig, E. M." box="[619,781,871,897]" pageId="79" pageNumber="80" pagination="123 - 154" refId="ref87582" refString="Danzig, E. M. (2001) Mealybugs of the genera Peliococcus and Peliococcopsis from Russia and neighbouring countries (Homoptera: Coccinea: Pseudococcidae). Zoosystematica Rossica, 9 (1), 123 - 154." type="journal article" year="2001">Danzig (2001)</bibRefCitation>
had clusters of multilocular pores on all body segments.
</paragraph>
